id: pm-cbwg
title: "SDK-only exemplar: minimal custom PM CLI package proving the universal-tool story end-to-end"
description: "A packages/ exemplar (e.g. pm-minimal) that assembles a working project-specific PM tool importing only @unbrained/pm-cli/sdk — custom types/statuses via schema primitives, custom commands via lifecycle/query primitives — serving as living documentation and the acceptance proof for story pm-w89s. Duplicate check: existing exemplars (pm-kanban etc.) demonstrate extension authoring, not SDK-only tool assembly."
type: Feature
status: closed
priority: 2
