acceptance_criteria: "Exemplar package builds+tests using only public SDK imports; exercises lifecycle, query, annotations, governance, schema customization; linked tests run in CI; referenced from SDK docs as the build-your-own-PM-tool guide"
parent: pm-usfg
risk: low
confidence: medium
resolution: Delivered a package-shaped SDK-only universal project tool exemplar and public guide.
expected_result: "A copyable consumer uses only the public SDK for customization, lifecycle, queries, context, annotations, relationships, and governance."
actual_result: Linked acceptance tests and an installed-tarball temporary consumer pass every required primitive with no CLI or private-core import.
